headline: Corrections & Amplifications
summary: CORRECTIONS Dominas, a skin-care brand from South Korea, was misspelled as Dominus in a Journal Report article on Thursday about facial treatments. Elliott Investment Management got less than 20% of Phillips 66’s employee pension fund voting in favor of its four nominees on the refiner’s board.
